data.description: Investor friendly - Rent ready in deep South SATX! This well-kept 3 bed, 2 bath, full of upgrades, is a slam dunk for the wise investor. Nestled snugly between 410/281 and easy access to IH37. This one won't last! CALL TODAY!! (CASH or HML ONLY) Needs to close before end of January.    Open floor plan, split bedrooms, porcelain tile throughout, custom cabinets, granite counter tops, backsplash, custom bathrooms, porch in front and back, 40ft Cement Drive way.
